Initialize the PS

```
1. Load ps7_init. tcl using the command “source ps7_init. ...
2. Use the “connect” command to connect to the Zedboard.
3. Use the “targets” command to get a list of targets (you could skip this).
4. Use the command “target 1” to select your target.
5. Call “ps_init” and then “ps_post_config”.
6. The PS is now initialized.
```



